OL,3,CDriver who rammed truck into
OL,4,Cgirlfriend jailed for life
OL,6,FA recovery truck driver has been
OL,7,Fsentenced to life in prison for murder.
OL,9,FMohammed Azim killed his teenage
OL,10,Fgirlfriend Lily Whitehouse by crushing
OL,11,Fher against a lamppost in Oldbury with
OL,12,Fhis truck.
OL,14,FHe will serve a minimum term of 20
OL,15,Fyears.
OL,17,FAzim, who is 41, murdered 19-year-old
OL,18,FLily Whitehouse in Oldbury in November
OL,19,Flast year on his 41st birthday on
OL,20,FNovember 5.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
