OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782233278
OL,3,CDriver who rammed truck into
OL,4,Cgirlfriend jailed for life
OL,6,FJurors took less than six hours to
OL,7,Ffind Mohammed Azim guilty by a
OL,8,Fmajority of 10 to two of murder on
OL,9,FFriday after a two-week trial at
OL,10,FWolverhampton Crown Court.
OL,12,FLily, who has been described as "full
OL,13,Fof light, laughter, and kindness," had
OL,14,Fjust returned from visiting her new
OL,15,Fbaby in hospital.
OL,17,FThe baby had been born prematurely and
OL,18,Fwas in the neo-natal intensive care
OL,19,Funit at Russells Hall Hospital.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
