OL,3,CDriver who rammed truck into
OL,4,Cgirlfriend jailed for life
OL,6,FThe pair had started dating when she
OL,7,Fwas 16 and he was 37 and had an on-off
OL,8,Frelationship. Lily had her baby with
OL,9,Fanother man.
OL,11,FOn 5 November 2025, Lily rang Azim
OL,12,Fafter her hospital visit and he picked
OL,13,Fher up. It's thought they argued, and
OL,14,FLily got out of the truck before Azim
OL,15,Fchased her down and drove the vehicle
OL,16,Finto her.
OL,18,FCCTV footage captured him pushing her
OL,19,Fwith his truck and then, off camera,
OL,20,Fit's thought he pinned her against a
OL,21,Flamppost - which killed her.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
