PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782233278
OL,3,CDriver who rammed truck into
OL,4,Cgirlfriend jailed for life
OL,6,FPassing sentence on Monday, Judge Mr
OL,7,FJustice Murray said: "Your decision to
OL,8,Fkill Lily was spontaneous, but you
OL,9,Fwould have been aware she had a five-
OL,10,Fweek-old baby still in hospital.
OL,12,F"The baby has lost her mother forever
OL,13,Fat the very beginning of her life.
OL,15,F"Although Lily was not particularly
OL,16,Fvulnerable... she was a
OL,17,Fpsychologically vulnerable young woman
OL,18,Fgiven her troubled background.
OL,20,F"She was very needy and dependent on
OL,21,Fyou as you well knew."
OL,26,@oD@VOUtD@AOUwD@AOU|D@AOU}D@VO]
