OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782233278
OL,3,CDriver who rammed truck into
OL,4,Cgirlfriend jailed for life
OL,6,FHe added: "It must have been apparent
OL,7,Fat the moment you drove your heavy
OL,8,Ftruck at her, there was a substantial
OL,9,Frisk you could kill her by doing so.
OL,11,F"I cannot be sure you formed an
OL,12,Fintention to kill Lily when you hit
OL,13,Fher with your truck.
OL,15,F"I sentence on a basis that you
OL,16,Fintention was to cause her really
OL,17,Fserious harm."
